Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人回个话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运输机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人到达D岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Festum…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗 援军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只知道消除这一件事 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然受Festum的保护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些被同化的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要全部杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要救到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打中人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援的Fafner？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离20
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner部队 遇敌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量艾欧罗斯型正在散开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:53.80,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(579,663)}Euros
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的核觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我们更快赶到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速击退敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚瑠岛部队前往救援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然躲在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冻起来同化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四号机…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲洋？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会守护大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见…学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿晖 听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿晖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛…来救我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 思考联系同步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿晖 大家在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人…把远见学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快去…救她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕获D岛机体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海因茨和一艘辅助机被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求发射暴君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.27,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(719,663)}Tyrant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算全部付之一炬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还算是人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:06:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类创造的火吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不想被烧掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是人渣啊 这些人类军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊
