Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来主操 和之前的存在一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我救了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以同化你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样答应他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 好高兴能获得你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是还不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等全世界都和平了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人再悲伤痛苦了 才能吃掉美羽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这之前你要帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我也能拜托你一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认5001名生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珀耳修斯中队 9成死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机库发来报告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已收容Nicht及十号机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mk.Sein也已回收
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mk.Sein…怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有生命反应 尽快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好严重的同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人早动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援没来的话真的很险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是御门叔给你们做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦给我以近藤咲良的名义重新登录
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你们 婚礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在神社办过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望大家都在场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广登和远见竟然被掳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:11:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的人类军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我没能追上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有交涉的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我想和你们谈谈机体的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡诺恩在机库吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡诺恩…不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经不在…任何地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个果然是美三香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她仅剩的一点心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成这样还去…你真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是差点就末期症状了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有多乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为我们派来了自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千言万语也不足以表达感谢和歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他像他母亲 会坚定走完自己相信的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我也只能目送他离去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有办法救他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用星核的因子 他一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛会祝福一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一骑希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核的祝福？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能说人类的话语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能让你的星核扎根在岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为星核之间会互相同化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他的新天地可以扎根
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算去何处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被新联合国埋葬的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三ALVIS
