Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在与虚无的地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛的祝福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所憎恨的Mk.Nicht
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是只属于你的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为希望而存在 不能舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是交涉需要它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢和世界 你选择救哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者都救
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让岛的核失望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我的名字 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请允许我出岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接受祝福之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命似乎还不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使消失之后 你的生命一定还会延续
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说星核所给予的死与再生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当新的星核扎根于另一座岛时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你的容器将重生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了那样的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不应该告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你一定会不惧未来 到达彼方的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想像普通家庭一样一起生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈祷未来能实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我们存在过的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士学长 你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能带他回来 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到希望了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生还到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能救回广登和远见学姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定带他们回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:15:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 居然是个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光弘？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为新联合国的间谍 怎么有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和被敌人同化的家伙们一起待过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以脑子有毛病了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,间谍？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你这丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:16:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是哥哥 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里换 动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然毙了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:27.02,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(70,30)}别磨磨蹭蹭的 对了 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她住手 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她击坠了轰炸机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有当场枪毙就算她好运了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D岛的人都移植了敌人的因子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你几时会放金光啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光弘·巴特蓝的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有胆识 够冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是新联合国秘书长 赫丝特·盖洛普
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拜托你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是驾驶Fafner吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真明理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前父亲也这么希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救世主模型 Mk.Raison
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做其测试驾驶员就让你免罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免去杀害诚实勇敢的人类军士兵的重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了五号机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的同伴怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说有回收其遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们杀了他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是在战场上牺牲的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对光弘做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光弘？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那个傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有知情的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普罗米修斯之岩窟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有极少数人能进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的圣域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去在日本发现的濑户内海星核被一分为三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由三座ALVIS进行管理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这曾是其一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三ALVIS·亚特兰蒂斯之核
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ALVIS？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是其他存在的核
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒谢尔型·流浪者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:26.91,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(758,663)}Vagrant
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天堂之门作战中我们所获得的星核变异体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界唯一一座宇宙空间站
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用卫星通信 诱导敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我们的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外 巴特蓝的研究还催生了各种成果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡也是其一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光弘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓傀儡 就是这个核的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:21:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生为各种形态 为流浪者传送情报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能自由操纵 方便的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是巴特蓝制造的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我们透露情报 削弱了纳雷因的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 我听你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强行操纵傀儡 其人格迟早会崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是让他从痛苦中解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光弘·巴特蓝的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类军的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告普罗米修斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹消傀儡MB7的人格
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心灵…在消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.78,0:22:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要知道很多事 真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了继承你父亲的遗志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上头有令让你从今天起使用这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我回原来的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.86,0:22:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗就会被洗脑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺从接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了回同伴身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.54,0:22:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丧失希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.84,0:23:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待和你连接
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙制造了许多心灵 又将其抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所在的岛上的人们 也都被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.53,0:23:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当此时 力量都会成长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 诞生了你这个容器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们大家的憎恨之容器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.13,0:24:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.53,0:24:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…！
